Fields.Description: Link to the submission for the process in Automation Hub

Fields.Name: ProcessDescription
Fields.Description: Description of the process from Automation Hub if it exists

Fields.Name: ProcessFolder
Fields.Description: The Orchestrator folder where the process is located. This is used for filtering/querying for a specific folder

Entities.Name: ProgramMetrics
Entities.Description: Program level metrics for the AREP_ProgramCentral App

Fields.Name: TotalJobsRun
Fields.Description: The number of jobs run across all the processes. This is a sum of the job count across all the process statistics entries

Fields.Name: InUseProcessesDisplay
Fields.Description: Display value for processes in use

Fields.Name: TotalJobsRunDisplay
Fields.Description: Display value for total jobs run

Fields.Name: DisplayID
Fields.Description: ID to use so we can lookup and return one entity

Fields.Name: HoursSavedDisplay
Fields.Description: Display value for hours saved for the company

Fields.Name: AutomatedProcesses
Fields.Description: Number of automations deployed in production

Entities.Name: Top10Users
Entities.Description: Stores the top 10 users based on job runs. This is used to display the top 10 users in order in the AREP Program Framework App

Fields.Name: ActivityRank
Fields.Description: Integer ranking the activity of the user. 1 is the most active

Fields.Name: DisplayName
Fields.Description: Name displayed for the user in the App

Entities.Name: AppsUsage
Entities.Description: Entity that holds information regarding the apps accessed.

Entities.Name: UserMetrics
Entities.Description: Metrics specific to each user in the cloud about their activity with UiPath shown in the AREP_ProgramCentral App

Fields.Name: PublishCheck
Fields.Description: Yes/no field describing if the user has received a check for publishing an app

Fields.Name: ConnectCheck
Fields.Description: Yes/no field describing if the user has received a check for interacting with the connect page

Fields.Name: AcceptBuildTerms
Fields.Description: Yes/no field describing if the user agreed to accept build terms.

Fields.Name: JobsRunDisplay
Fields.Description: Display value for jobs run per user

Fields.Name: ActivityRankDisplay
Fields.Description: Display value for user's activity rank

Fields.Name: BuildCheck
Fields.Description: Yes/no field describing if the user received the check for building an automation

Fields.Name: ExploreCheck
Fields.Description: Yes/no field describing if the user received the check for exploring the program

Fields.Name: InvolveCheck
Fields.Description: Yes/no field describing if the user received the check for getting involved in the program

Fields.Name: RunCheck
Fields.Description: Yes/no field describing if the user received the check for running an automation

Fields.Name: SubmitCheck
Fields.Description: Yes/no field describing if the user received the check for submitting an idea

Fields.Name: TrainCheck
Fields.Description: Yes/no field describing if the user received the check for completing training

Fields.Name: UserType
Fields.Description: Value of either runner or developer indicating whether the user will just be running automations or also developing them

Fields.Name: SavedTime
Fields.Description: The estimated number of minutes the user has saved by running automations

Fields.Name: IsDeveloper
Fields.Description: Yes /no field to describe if the user is a developer and on the Cit Dev path in AREP App

Fields.Name: Training1Complete
Fields.Description: Yes/no value indicating if the user completed training 1

Fields.Name: Training2Complete
Fields.Description: Yes/no value indicating if the user completed training 2

Fields.Name: Training3Complete
Fields.Description: Yes/no value indicating if the user completed training 3

Entities.Name: Top10Autos
Entities.Description: Stores the top 10 automations based on runs. This is used to display the top 10 automations in order in the AREP Program Framework App

Fields.Name: FirstLetter
Fields.Description: First letter of the display name. Used in the AREP portal app

Fields.Name: ProcessDescription
Fields.Description: Description of the process from Automation Hub if it exists

Fields.Name: TimeSaveDisplay
Fields.Description: Display value for how much time the process has saved
